    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unify Medieval Japan in this real-time tactical grand strategy game. Build your domain, recruit armies, plan your attack, and fracture your enemies with rebellions to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/59fce8bce78d3b28eaa1460aa18e741e.poster.avif?t=1768678211\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/59fce8bce78d3b28eaa1460aa18e741e.webm?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/59fce8bce78d3b28eaa1460aa18e741e.mp4?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Build</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Building improvements allow you to increase your wealth, recruit new units, defend your territory, and reduce unrest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/88bf20715027c42f976e14d9c5998075.poster.avif?t=1768678211\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/88bf20715027c42f976e14d9c5998075.webm?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/88bf20715027c42f976e14d9c5998075.mp4?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Plan</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Pause the game at any time to plan coordinated attacks with your armies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/4665a8917a8e3e5ea83c8c7b48305d98.poster.avif?t=1768678211\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/4665a8917a8e3e5ea83c8c7b48305d98.webm?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/4665a8917a8e3e5ea83c8c7b48305d98.mp4?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Conquer</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Conduct real-time tactical assaults with your armies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/39e8b74aa139686aa41ab3602c52a03b.poster.avif?t=1768678211\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/39e8b74aa139686aa41ab3602c52a03b.webm?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/39e8b74aa139686aa41ab3602c52a03b.mp4?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Survive</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fight off internal rebellions threatening your domain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/be7fb48cceaa5b6d66d25319badff280.poster.avif?t=1768678211\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034170/extras/be7fb48cceaa5b6d66d25319badff280.webm?t=1768678211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item